🚀 Benefits of This Approach

Feature	Benefit
✅ Stores Request ID in MDC	Automatically available in all logs.
✅ Filters only selected fields	Reduces memory usage and logs only useful data.
✅ Supports nested JSON fields	Extracts specific fields from objects like address.postalCode.
✅ Ensures MDC is cleared after request	Prevents data leaks across requests.
✅ Configurable fields via properties	No hardcoding required.

